Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…祝你早日康復
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.41,0:00:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得我喜歡什麼花哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 突然叫你來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.34,0:00:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合唱部在今年的比賽中又得金獎了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了報紙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不叫合唱部了 叫聲樂部
